    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Tanytarsus meta sp. nov., male. A, B: hypopygium in dorsal (A) and ventral aspect (B); C: anal tergite and anal point; D: superior volsella and digitus; E, F: median volsella photographed (E) and drawn (F); (C–F magnified ca. 2–3 times relative to A and B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6504156/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

